Costco customer service contacts - Elliott





















































 










 Elliott
A site that advocates for you










Costco


Costco Wholesale Corporation is a multinational company with headquarters in Washington. The company allows customers to obtain memberships to buy bulk goods in a warehouse setting. Products sold are not limited to toys, food, electronics, alcohol, house wares, jewelry and office supplies.
999 Lake DriveSuite 200Issaquah, WA 98027http://www.costco.comPhone ContactsMain: (425) 313-8100Customer Service: (800) 955-2292Toll Free: (800) 774-2678Company fax:  (425) 427-7520
Company tech support for electronics:  (866) 861-0450
How to get through to a person.
Press “55” at the prompt.
Email Contacts memberservice@costco.comCustomer Service ResourcesContact Us page
Social Media Contacts Facebook Twitter Google PlusThe company is typically more responsive on Twitter.
Executive ContactsPrimary ContactKelsey BerryManager999 Lake DriveSuite 200Issaquah, WA 98027(425) 427-3539Kberry@costco.comSecondary ContactJohn McKayExecutive Vice President999 Lake DriveSuite 200Issaguah, WA 98027JMckay@costco.comChief ExecutiveW. Craig JelinekChief Executive Officer999 Lake DriveSuite 200Issaquah, WA 98027(425) 313-8100cjelinek@costco.comResearched by Eva Dickerson and filed under Retail.Last updated: January 17, 2017.






